{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/TIL/0110/","result":{"data":{"cur":{"id":"ab83d630-9bf2-5734-83f0-46eb5ce05b5e","html":"<h2 id=\"typescript-타이핑-과정-중에-발생한-에러\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#typescript-%ED%83%80%EC%9D%B4%ED%95%91-%EA%B3%BC%EC%A0%95-%EC%A4%91%EC%97%90-%EB%B0%9C%EC%83%9D%ED%95%9C-%EC%97%90%EB%9F%AC\" aria-label=\"typescript 타이핑 과정 중에 발생한 에러 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>TypeScript 타이핑 과정 중에 발생한 에러</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 708px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 41.11111111111111%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1.png\"\n        title=\"1.png\"\n        src=\"/static/e4c8d1f4a01dcd495d71d3a0f1f58472/3cb0f/1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e4c8d1f4a01dcd495d71d3a0f1f58472/e9ff0/1.png 180w,\n/static/e4c8d1f4a01dcd495d71d3a0f1f58472/f21e7/1.png 360w,\n/static/e4c8d1f4a01dcd495d71d3a0f1f58472/3cb0f/1.png 708w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 708px) 100vw, 708px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>사실 ESLint에서 발생하는 오류라서 실행은 정상적으로 되지만, 거슬리기 때문에 해결하기 위해 구글링을 했다.\r\n<br/></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"해결방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"해결방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>해결방법</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>먼저, ESLint 자체에서 해결하기 위해 .eslint.js를 연다.</li>\n<li>다음과 같은 문구를 추가한다.</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">  rules: {\r\n        'prettier/prettier': [\r\n            'error',\r\n            {\r\n                endOfLine: 'auto',\r\n            },\r\n        ],\r\n    },</code></pre></div>\n<br/>\r\n다음과 같이 에러가 해결되었다!   \r\n<br/>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 711px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 41.11111111111111%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2.png\"\n        title=\"2.png\"\n        src=\"/static/960120b3924f1cb2f91d6043c38103ff/a8e5b/2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/960120b3924f1cb2f91d6043c38103ff/e9ff0/2.png 180w,\n/static/960120b3924f1cb2f91d6043c38103ff/f21e7/2.png 360w,\n/static/960120b3924f1cb2f91d6043c38103ff/a8e5b/2.png 711w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 711px) 100vw, 711px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>","excerpt":"TypeScript 타이핑 과정 중에 발생한 에러  사실 ESLint에서 발생하는 오류라서 실행은 정상적으로 되지만, 거슬리기 때문에 해결하기 위해 구글링을 했다.\r\n 해결방법 먼저, ESLint 자체에서 해결하기 위해 .eslint.js를 연다. 다음과 같은 문구를 추가한다.","frontmatter":{"date":"January 10, 2023","title":"Delete `␍`eslintprettier/prettier","categories":"Error, TypeScript","author":"권형석","emoji":"👾"},"fields":{"slug":"/TIL/0110/"}},"next":{"id":"4fb8113a-55a5-54c6-9c48-95bfd8a47c5b","html":"<h4 id=\"기존에-사용했던-recoil-이외의-전역상태관리-라이브러리인-redux를-학습하며-정리합니다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B8%B0%EC%A1%B4%EC%97%90-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%96%88%EB%8D%98-recoil-%EC%9D%B4%EC%99%B8%EC%9D%98-%EC%A0%84%EC%97%AD%EC%83%81%ED%83%9C%EA%B4%80%EB%A6%AC-%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%8C%EB%9F%AC%EB%A6%AC%EC%9D%B8-redux%EB%A5%BC-%ED%95%99%EC%8A%B5%ED%95%98%EB%A9%B0-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC%ED%95%A9%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"기존에 사용했던 recoil 이외의 전역상태관리 라이브러리인 redux를 학습하며 정리합니다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>기존에 사용했던 recoil 이외의 전역상태관리 라이브러리인 redux를 학습하며 정리합니다.</h4>\n<h1 id=\"useselector\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#useselector\" aria-label=\"useselector permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>useSelector()</h1>\n<p>useSelector는 Redux store로부터 state를 가져올 때 사용한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">import {createStore} from \"redux\";\r\n\r\nconst store = createStore(reducer);\r\n\r\nexport default store;\r\n</code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"usedispatch\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#usedispatch\" aria-label=\"usedispatch permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>useDispatch()</h1>\n<p>useDispatch는 action을 reducer로 dispatch할 때 사용할 수 있는 훅이다. (reducer로 dispatch하여 기존의 state를 <code class=\"language-text\">대체</code>한다)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">import {useDispatch} from \"react-redux\"\r\n\r\nconst dispatch = useDispatch();\r\n\r\ndispatch(ACTION)</code></pre></div>\n<hr/>\n<h3 id=\"리덕스-작업을-위해서는-3개의-파일을-생성해야-한다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A6%AC%EB%8D%95%EC%8A%A4-%EC%9E%91%EC%97%85%EC%9D%84-%EC%9C%84%ED%95%B4%EC%84%9C%EB%8A%94-3%EA%B0%9C%EC%9D%98-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC%EC%9D%84-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1%ED%95%B4%EC%95%BC-%ED%95%9C%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"리덕스 작업을 위해서는 3개의 파일을 생성해야 한다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>리덕스 작업을 위해서는 3개의 파일을 생성해야 한다.</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<li/>action   \n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>action을 생성하고, 해당 action이 어떤 일을 수행할지 지정한다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<li/>reducer   \n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>dispatch된 action을 실행시킬 reducer\r\naction 객체를 받아 기존의 state를 대체시킨다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<li/>store   \n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>reducer로 <code class=\"language-text\">global store</code>를 만든다</p>\n</blockquote>\n<br/>\n<h4 id=\"간단한-todo-list를-만들기-위해-todo를-추가하고-삭제하는-action을-만든다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%84%EB%8B%A8%ED%95%9C-todo-list%EB%A5%BC-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EA%B8%B0-%EC%9C%84%ED%95%B4-todo%EB%A5%BC-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80%ED%95%98%EA%B3%A0-%EC%82%AD%EC%A0%9C%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-action%EC%9D%84-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A0%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"간단한 todo list를 만들기 위해 todo를 추가하고 삭제하는 action을 만든다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>간단한 todo-list를 만들기 위해 todo를 추가하고 삭제하는 action을 만든다.</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">export const add_todo = (todo) => {\r\n    return {\r\n        type:ADD,\r\n        todo:{\r\n            id: id++,\r\n            title: todo.title,\r\n            isComplete: todo.isComplete,\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n};\r\n\r\nexport const delete_todo = (id) => {\r\n    return {\r\n        type: DELETE,\r\n        id,\r\n    }\r\n};</code></pre></div>\n<p>todo를 추가하기위해 매개변수로 받은 todo 객체를 reducer에게 반환하고, todo를 삭제하기 위해서는 삭제하려는 todo의 id만을 넘겨준다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">const initialState = {\r\n    todos:[],\r\n};\r\n\r\n// action을 받아서 새로운 객체를 형성하고, store의 객체를 대체한다\r\nexport const reducers = (state = initialState, action) => {\r\n    if (action.type === ADD){\r\n        return{\r\n            todos:[...state.todos, action.todo],\r\n        };\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    if (action.type === DELETE) {\r\n        return {\r\n            todos:[...state.todos.filter((todo) => todo.id !== action.id)]\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n\r\n}</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">[ADD]</code>initialState로 todos라는 빈 배열을 만들고, 이 배열에 새로운 항목을 추가한 <code class=\"language-text\">새로운 state</code>를 반환하도록 한다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">[DELETE]</code>action이 넘겨줄 id를 가지고 <code class=\"language-text\">Array.filter()</code> 메서드를 이용해 id가 동일한 todo 객체를 삭제한 todos를 반환하도록 한다.`</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"store\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#store\" aria-label=\"store permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>store</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">import {createStore} from \"redux\";\r\n\r\nconst store = createStore(reducer);\r\n\r\nexport default store;</code></pre></div>\n<p>리덕스 store에 reducer를 넣어주는 작업을 해당 파일에서 수행한다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"inputform\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#inputform\" aria-label=\"inputform permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>InputForm</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">export default function InputForm() {\r\n\r\n    const dispatch = useDispatch();\r\n    const [text, setText] = useState(\"\");\r\n\r\n    const handleChange = (e: any) => {\r\n        const {value} = e.target;\r\n        setText(value);\r\n        // console.log(\"text\", text)\r\n    };\r\n\r\n    const handleClick = () => {\r\n        if (text.trim() === ''){\r\n            alert(\"글자를 입력해주세요\");\r\n            return;\r\n        };\r\n        const todo = {\r\n            title: text,\r\n            isComplete:false,\r\n        }\r\n        // action을 dispatch\r\n        dispatch(add_todo(todo));\r\n        alert(\"입력되었습니다\");\r\n        setText(\"\");\r\n\r\n    };\r\n\r\n    const handleKeyPress = (e:any) => {\r\n        if(e.key === \"Enter\"){\r\n            handleClick();\r\n        }\r\n    };\r\n\r\n\r\n  return (\r\n    &lt;Wrapper>\r\n        &lt;Input placeholder='Write down your todos' onChange={handleChange} onKeyDown={handleKeyPress}/>\r\n        &lt;Buttons onClick={handleClick}>Add&lt;/Buttons>\r\n    &lt;/Wrapper>\r\n  )\r\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"todoitem\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#todoitem\" aria-label=\"todoitem permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>todoItem</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">export default function TodoItem({todo}) {\r\n    const dispatch = useDispatch();\r\n\r\n    const {id, title, isComplete} = todo;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n    // action(delete_todo)을 dispatch한다.\r\n    const handleClick = () => {\r\n        dispatch(delete_todo(id))\r\n    }\r\n  return (\r\n    &lt;Wrapper>\r\n      &lt;input type=\"checkbox\" onClick={handleCheck}/>\r\n        &lt;Title>{title}&lt;/Title>\r\n        {/* &lt;div onClick={handleClick}>x&lt;/div> */}\r\n        &lt;IconWrapper>\r\n          &lt;BsPen style={{cursor:'pointer', marginRight:'20px'}}/>\r\n          &lt;BsTrash onClick={handleClick} style={{cursor:'pointer'}}/>\r\n        &lt;/IconWrapper>\r\n    &lt;/Wrapper>\r\n  )\r\n}</code></pre></div>\n<p>여기에서는 todo item을 삭제, 즉 해당 todo를 완료했을 경우를 위해 DELETE ACTION을 dispatch한다. 이를 위해 useDispatch()를 사용했다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"todolist\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#todolist\" aria-label=\"todolist permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>todoList</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">export default function TodoList() {\r\n    const todos = useSelector((state:any) => state?.todos);\r\n\r\n  return (\r\n        &lt;Wrapper>\r\n          {todos?.map((todo:any) => (\r\n              &lt;TodoItem key={todo.id} todo={todo}>&lt;/TodoItem>\r\n          ))}\r\n         &lt;/Wrapper>\r\n    \r\n  )\r\n}</code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"date":"January 10, 2023","title":"Redux로 todo-list 만들기","categories":"Redux","author":"권형석","emoji":"📚"},"fields":{"slug":"/redux/0110/"}},"prev":{"id":"b95f9f2f-c6da-590d-a586-01f58e44eada","html":"<h1 id=\"context-api\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#context-api\" aria-label=\"context api permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Context api</h1>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 65.55555555555556%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1.png\"\n        title=\"1.png\"\n        src=\"/static/6881653e4907e5355beed0cf27f8214f/37523/1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6881653e4907e5355beed0cf27f8214f/e9ff0/1.png 180w,\n/static/6881653e4907e5355beed0cf27f8214f/f21e7/1.png 360w,\n/static/6881653e4907e5355beed0cf27f8214f/37523/1.png 720w,\n/static/6881653e4907e5355beed0cf27f8214f/302a4/1.png 1080w,\n/static/6881653e4907e5355beed0cf27f8214f/07a9c/1.png 1440w,\n/static/6881653e4907e5355beed0cf27f8214f/891d5/1.png 1520w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>매우 많은 컴포넌트들이 존재한다면 props를 넘겨줄 때 props drilling 현상이 일어날 수 있다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>props는 자신의 부모 컴포넌트로부터 받는 데이터이고, 단방향의 성질을 가진다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<br/>\r\n<br/>\n<blockquote>\n<h4 id=\"️-만약-컴포넌트들의-구조가-매우-복잡해서-code-classlanguage-text1번-컴포넌트의-자식-컴포넌트---자식의-자식-컴포넌트---code-로-컴포넌트가-중첩되어-있는-구조인-상태라면\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EF%B8%8F-%EB%A7%8C%EC%95%BD-%EC%BB%B4%ED%8F%AC%EB%84%8C%ED%8A%B8%EB%93%A4%EC%9D%98-%EA%B5%AC%EC%A1%B0%EA%B0%80-%EB%A7%A4%EC%9A%B0-%EB%B3%B5%EC%9E%A1%ED%95%B4%EC%84%9C-code-classlanguage-text1%EB%B2%88-%EC%BB%B4%ED%8F%AC%EB%84%8C%ED%8A%B8%EC%9D%98-%EC%9E%90%EC%8B%9D-%EC%BB%B4%ED%8F%AC%EB%84%8C%ED%8A%B8---%EC%9E%90%EC%8B%9D%EC%9D%98-%EC%9E%90%EC%8B%9D-%EC%BB%B4%ED%8F%AC%EB%84%8C%ED%8A%B8---code-%EB%A1%9C-%EC%BB%B4%ED%8F%AC%EB%84%8C%ED%8A%B8%EA%B0%80-%EC%A4%91%EC%B2%A9%EB%90%98%EC%96%B4-%EC%9E%88%EB%8A%94-%EA%B5%AC%EC%A1%B0%EC%9D%B8-%EC%83%81%ED%83%9C%EB%9D%BC%EB%A9%B4\" aria-label=\"️ 만약 컴포넌트들의 구조가 매우 복잡해서 code classlanguage text1번 컴포넌트의 자식 컴포넌트   자식의 자식 컴포넌트   code 로 컴포넌트가 중첩되어 있는 구조인 상태라면 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>☠️ 만약 컴포넌트들의 구조가 매우 복잡해서, <code class=\"language-text\">1번 컴포넌트의 자식 컴포넌트 -> 자식의 자식 컴포넌트 -> ....</code> 로 컴포넌트가 중첩되어 있는 구조인 상태라면?</h4>\n</blockquote>\n<br/>\r\n<br/>\n<p>props만으로 전달받아 후순위의 컴포넌트에서 사용한다면, 그 사이에 있는 어마어마하게 많은 컴포넌트는 단순한 <code class=\"language-text\">데이터 다리</code>역할을 하는것이다.</p>\n<br/>\r\n<br/>\n<p><strong> 이때 Context API를 통해, 즉 전역상태를 통해 이러한 문제점을 해결할 수 있다.<strong/></p>\n<ul>\n<li>_app.ts 파일에서 context Provider로 컴포넌트의 최상위부분을 묶어준다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">[_app.tsx]\r\n\r\nimport { createContext, useContext } from \"react\";\r\n\r\nexport const MyContext = createContext();\r\n\r\nfunction MyApp({ Component, pageProps }) {\r\n return (\r\n   &lt;MyContext.Provider value=\"안녕안녕안녕\">\r\n     &lt;Component {...pageProps} />\r\n   &lt;/MyContext.Provider>\r\n );\r\n}\r\n\r\nexport default MyApp;</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>그 이후, MyContext의 value를 받아 사용할 컴포넌트에서 useContext 훅을 이용해 정의한 context를 불러와서 사용하면 된다.</li>\n<li>props로 값을 넘겨받지 않고도 전역적으로 value를 불러올 수 있다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">import React from \"react\";\r\nimport { useContext } from \"react\";\r\nimport { MyContext } from \"../../../../pages/_app\";\r\n\r\nexport default function First() {\r\n const value = useContext(MyContext);\r\n return &lt;div>{value}&lt;/div>;\r\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"정보를-찾아보며-전역상태관리-라이브러리들도-context-api를-활용하여-만들어졌다는것을-알게되었다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%95%EB%B3%B4%EB%A5%BC-%EC%B0%BE%EC%95%84%EB%B3%B4%EB%A9%B0-%EC%A0%84%EC%97%AD%EC%83%81%ED%83%9C%EA%B4%80%EB%A6%AC-%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%8C%EB%9F%AC%EB%A6%AC%EB%93%A4%EB%8F%84-context-api%EB%A5%BC-%ED%99%9C%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EC%97%AC-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EC%96%B4%EC%A1%8C%EB%8B%A4%EB%8A%94%EA%B2%83%EC%9D%84-%EC%95%8C%EA%B2%8C%EB%90%98%EC%97%88%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"정보를 찾아보며 전역상태관리 라이브러리들도 context api를 활용하여 만들어졌다는것을 알게되었다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>정보를 찾아보며 전역상태관리 라이브러리들도 context API를 활용하여 만들어졌다는것을 알게되었다.</h4>\n<br/>\r\n<br/>\n<ul>\n<li>기존에 사용하던 recoil도 컴포넌트들을 RecoilRoot로 묶어주는 방식을 통해 전역으로 상태를 관리했었는데, 고개가 끄덕여지는 부분.</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"date":"January 12, 2023","title":"Context API","categories":"ContextAPI,전역상태관리","author":"권형석","emoji":"🪐"},"fields":{"slug":"/TIL/0112/"}},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://hskwon5170.github.io","comments":{"utterances":{"repo":""}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/TIL/0110/","nextSlug":"/redux/0110/","prevSlug":"/TIL/0112/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1073350324","1956554647","2938748437"]}